{% macro about_link(style) %}
    <a style="{{ style }}" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#aboutModal">About us</a>
    <div style="text-align:left;font-weight:400;" class="modal fade" id="aboutModal" data-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="msg-modal-Label" aria-hidden="true" >
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-md">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span></button>
            <h4 class="modal-title" id="msg-modal-Label">About us</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <p style="white-space: pre-wrap;word-wrap: break-word;">
Nowadays you can find an incredible quantity of language learning apps and softwares&hellip;

While these tools are interesting resources for your language education, they still lack of real life like interactivity to provide you good conversation skills and self-confidence.

Farolang is an initiative to fill that (immense) gap by favoring people encounters all around the planet to help you learn and practice any language in a pleasant, efficient and affordable way. 

Hope you’ll enjoy it !

Farolang’s team <small>part of the ragondins’ collective</small>

Contact address : <a href="mailto:contactus@farolang.com">contactus@farolang.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro credit_link(style) %}
